>\n波台與成人台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n禾地波台氣fun巧巧。吾似duck cc台班噴精"},{"pid":"2d5ec0f48db2891c8d81e680e6771130f834a180","tid":86014,"uid":55712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T20:31:54.000Z","msg":"鳩up<br />\n腳重要啲定波重要啲既爭論可以鬥到香港建國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}